{"tid":1837580,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支那武漢緊急興建能容納千人病患貨櫃醫院連停屍間","createTime":"2020-01-23T16:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T16:42:05.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29c642112981315d83c3c0af63a46093d7893078","tid":1837580,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fj3utf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffj3utf3.jpg&h=22565f28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNiY52K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNiY52K.jpg&h=b458502d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVcrvuz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVcrvuz.jpg&h=5b2b87ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢市將在蔡甸區興建一個1000張病床（集裝箱）的新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎患者收治中心，這是一項需要短時間內完成的突擊任務。1月23日晚間，21世紀經濟報導記者獲悉，因為時間緊、任務重、要求高，且春節已經來臨，人力資源和物質資源匱乏，承建方和建設方需要緊急社會支援，以下為需求信息：<br />\n <br />\n1、中建三局因承建武漢市抗肺炎應急工程，需要護目鏡、防護服、醫用手套，醫用口罩等應急物品，有償採購，多多益善！<br />\n <br />\n2、另一個是面向武漢地區項目經理，因市政府要求三局在6天內在知音湖武漢職工療養院建一個新醫院，急需大小挖機若干、平板車數台、集裝箱好多，請武漢地區項目經理馬上動員項目資源，越快越好，越多越好！<br />\n <br />\n3、武漢建工集團向社會各界緊急徵集醫用口罩、醫用手套、免洗型洗手液及其他防護用品，請聯繫武漢建工集團工程管理部"},{"pid":"59b5d42dcf1dcfa4e202b4607f5b33ccad9ad4ed","tid":1837580,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工必須預演 刻不容緩 <br />\n<br />\n以而家既上升趨勢 點可能仲等到過完年先罷?<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工唔單止係阻止疫情<br />\n<br />\n要順勢爭取五大訴求, 唔好忘記:<br />\n<br />\n被捕 被自殺 被斬既手足<br />\n<br />\n仲等28號? 一定要預演, 否則會同1111一樣 即係西灣河槍殺人當日呀<br />\n<br />\n唔預演一陣到正日 得勁少人罷 雷聲大雨點小<br />\n<br />\n到時感染人數一定DOUBLE左<br />\n<br />\n剩係呢幾日都有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n另外再望下D相, 而家有籌碼都唔利用, 等幾時?<br />\n<br />\n仲想幾多手足死傷呀?<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O3j5yZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3j5yZP.png&h=a6e38b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpcfbMu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpcfbMu.jpg&h=7b2bceb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hzi2Bda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzi2Bda.jpg&h=e58944e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sDJ46w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sDJ46w.jpg&h=e0d1403c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgyBFES.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgyBFES.png&h=6cdaa886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dkb7NjS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkb7NjS.png&h=cea3c5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Akp5yZU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkp5yZU.png&h=903e310e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtFsNjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtFsNjV.png&h=89fcf619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbLknTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbLknTg.jpg&h=6347e0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p94JkEW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp94JkEW.jpg&h=fe14ef5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"714e2d59c11691e349765425229b1d665249ca04","tid":1837580,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0949cd167863928f9fbdf3b4a31de99de41f139","tid":1837580,"uid":311420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"好撚似喪屍片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse